entries.journal_entry_description: The Darkwalkers have another of the stolen Gungan artifacts.
entries.journal_entry_title: Recover the Gungan Artifact Stolen by the Darkwalkers
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The Darkwalkers have one of the stolen Gungan artifacts in their possession. Soften up the Darkwalker's defenses in the area by attacking some of them, so that you'll be able to recover the artifact.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Darkwalker Bloodlord Vran Tristen and recover the stolen artifact.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Defeat Vran Tristen, a Darkwalker Bloodlord
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Boss Nass with the artifact.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Da Darkwalker bloodlord, Vran Tristen, probably has da artifact. Probably.
